#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:2
msgid "DIP 桥接检测（DIP Bridge）"
msgstr "DIP Bridge Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:6
msgid "检测 DIP 器件相邻引脚 / 焊点之间的连锡。"
msgstr ""
"Detects solder bridges between adjacent leads or solder joints on DIP "
"components."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's"
" parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:14
msgid ""
"**桥接颜色公式（Bridge Color Formula）**：选择用于识别连锡的颜色公式（如 ``2B-R-G``）；选择三色时配置 **三色 X "
"/ Y / Z / A** 系数。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Color Formula**: choose the color formula used to detect solder "
"bridges (e.g. ``2B-R-G``); when **Tricolor** is chosen, configure **Tricolor"
" X / Y / Z / A**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:15
msgid "**灵敏度（Sensitivity）**：桥接颜色检测灵敏度（0–1），值越大检测范围越大。"
msgstr ""
"**Sensitivity**: sensitivity of the bridge color detection (0–1). Higher "
"values widen the detection band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:16
msgid "**桥接有效比率范围（Bridge Valid Ratio Range）**：连锡有效比例 OK 区间。"
msgstr "**Bridge Valid Ratio Range**: OK band for the bridge valid ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:17
msgid "**桥接宽度 (%)（Bridge Width）**：桥接检测带宽度。"
msgstr "**Bridge Width (%)**: width of the bridge-detection band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:18
msgid "**焊点数量（Solder Count）/ 焊点宽度 (mm)（Solder Width）**：焊点子框划分。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Count / Solder Width (mm)**: defines how the ROI is divided into "
"solder-joint sub-frames."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:19
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**。"
msgstr "**Enable Visualization**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:22
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_bridge.rst:26
msgid "**DIP 桥接敏感度怎么调**：与普通桥接相同 —— **灵敏度** 小时只抽蓝色，大时包含偏红像素。"
msgstr ""
"**How to tune DIP bridge sensitivity**: same advice as the standard Bridge "
"tool — a low **Sensitivity** picks up only blue pixels, while a high value "
"also includes reddish pixels."
